Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.46,0:01:27.50,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}aru ki tudu ke ta ima wo keshi te ha
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.50,0:01:31.88,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}mi nai you ni fusai da kako
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.88,0:01:35.64,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}kirisute rare te simaxtu ta kanousei
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.64,0:01:40.06,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}fukagyaku de saisei ha nido to kana wa nai
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.06,0:01:49.40,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}nando mo fukaku kizu tui ta kanasimi no hate (soredemo)
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.40,0:01:55.45,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}sinzou no kodou　kextu site to me nai you ni
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.45,0:02:03.50,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}koko kara　kimi to futari de no ri ko e te iku
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.50,0:02:09.71,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}meza si ta mirai he　sube te no kimi wo seo tte
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.71,0:02:12.92,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}tadori tu i te mi seru kara
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.92,0:02:18.22,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}taku sa re ta nega i wo　owara se te
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.22,0:02:24.10,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}kondo koso ha sube te mamo ru yo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.10,0:02:30.57,OPJPReL,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}saigo no unmei wo tuka me　realize
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:27.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}歩き続けた今を消しては
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:31.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}見ないように塞いだ過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:35.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}切り捨てられてしまった可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:40.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}不可逆で再生は二度と叶わない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:49.40,OPJP,,0,0,100,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}何度も深く傷ついた悲しみの果て (それでも)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:55.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}心臓の鼓動　決して止めないように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:02:03.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}ここから　君と二人で乗り越えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:09.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}目指した未来へ　全ての君を背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:12.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}たどり着いて見せるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:18.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}託された願いを　終わらせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:24.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}今度こそは全て守るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:30.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}最後の運命を掴め Realize
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:27.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}消除掉一路走来的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:31.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}当作尘封的过去  我不再回首
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:35.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}断然舍弃掉许多可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:40.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}只是选择不可逆  机会不会重临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:49.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}一次次深深受伤  痛苦至极 (但是)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:55.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我的心跳却永远不会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:02:03.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}接下来的困难  我要和你一同度过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:09.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}冲向目标的未来  背负起你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:12.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我一定会抵达那个终点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:18.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}完成你托付给我的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:24.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}这次我一定要守护住全部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:30.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}紧紧抓住最后的命运 Realize
